MALACAÑANG RESIDENCE OF THE PRESIDENT OF THE PHILIPPINES MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 260

RESERVING FOR ADMINISTRATION BUILDING AND DEMONSTRATION CENTER SITE PURPOSES OF THE SOCIAL WELFARE ADMINISTRATION CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF PAGADIAN, PROVINCE OF ZAMBOANGA DEL SUR, ISLAND OF MINDANAO.

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of Agriculture and Natural Resources and pursuant to the authority vested in me by law, I, FERDINAND E. MARCOS, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale and settlement and reserve for administration building and demonstration center site purposes under the administration of the Administrator of the Social Welfare Administration, subject to private rights, if any there be, certain parcels of land of the public domain situated in the municipality of Pagadian, Zamboanga del Sur, island of Mindanao, and more particularly described as follows:

Lot 2390

Pagadian, Pls-119, Case 1

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 2390 of Pagadian Pls-119), situated in the Poblacion, Municipality of Pagadian, Province of Zamboanga, Bounded on the NE. and SE., along lines 1-2-3, by Road; on the SW., along; lines 3-4-5, by Provincial Road; and on the NW., along line 5-1, by Lot 2391, Pagadian Pls-119. Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan, being N. 89 deg. 28’W., 484.31 m. from B.L.L.M. 3, Pagadian, Pls-119,

thence S. 12 deg. 35′ W., 19.47 m. to point 2;

thence S. 77 deg. 46′ W., 40.50 m. to point 3;

thence N. 55 deg. 37′ W., 4.14 m. to point 4;

thence N. 12 deg. 26′ W., 16.62 m. to point 5;

thence N. 72 deg. 59′ E., 43.29 m. to the point of

beginning; containing an area of EIGHT HUNDRED FORTY TWO (842) Square Meters.

